<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Transaction Alert</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo img {
            width: 150px; /* Adjust the size of your logo */
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .details {
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #292929;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #4caf50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #bbb;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #4caf50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        p{
            color:white!important;
        }

        .details > p{
            text-transform: capitalize;
            margin-top: 7px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img style="width:70px;height:70px" src="https://marketplace.crygoca.com/assets/_images/flutterwave-logo.png" alt="Company Logo">
        </div>

        <p>Dear <strong><%= data.walletTransaction.user.firstname %> <%= data.walletTransaction.user.lastname %></strong>,</p>
        <p>Outgoing <span class="highlight"><%= data.walletTransaction.user.geoData.currency.symbol %><%= Number(data.walletTransaction.amount).toFixed(2) %></span> transfer to <%= data.walletTransaction.creditWalletAccountNo %>.
           Your available balance is <span class="highlight"><%= data.walletTransaction.user.geoData.currency.symbol %><%= Number(data.wallet.balance).toFixed(2) %></span>.
        </p>

        <div class="details">
            <p class="title">Transfer Details:</p>
            <p><strong>To:</strong> <%= data.walletTransaction.creditWalletAccountNo %></p>
            <p><strong>Amount:</strong> <span class="highlight"><%= data.walletTransaction.user.geoData.currency.symbol %><%= Number(data.walletTransaction.amount).toFixed(2) %></span></p>
            <p><strong>Transaction Type:</strong> <%= data.walletTransaction.type.replaceAll("-", " ") %></p>
            <p><strong>Transaction No:</strong> <%= data.walletTransaction.reference %></p>
            <p><strong>Transaction Date:</strong> <%= data.walletTransaction.createdAt %></p>
        </div>

        <p>For further enquiries, please contact our customer support through the following channels:</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +44-273874848838</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@crygoca.com">support@crygoca.com</a></p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing <strong>Crygoca</strong>.</p>
            <p>The Crygoca Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
